title: Openstreetmap, Sachsen-Anhalt Natural Areas, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Sachsen-Anhalt Natural Areas, Germany, 2008
description: This data was provided by Openstreetmaps and contains detailed information on the Natural Areas in the Sachsen-Anhalt administrative area in Germany. Natural areas include parks, forests, riverbanks, and water. Data was uploaded as a poly line shape file and contains attributes for the feature type and the feature name when available.
